name: WFM RD&A Data
tagline: The Source for Geospatial Data Information
body:
### Welcome to Our Data Page.
In an effort to provide our users with with best available data we are utilizing this github page to publish data information. Here you will find the latest and greatest WFDSS, IFTDSS, and general wildland fire data information. Please check back regularly as we will be updating the site frequently.

### Contact Us
If you have questions about the contents of this page please contact:
Ben Butler (@wfmrdamaps)
WFDSS GIS Specialist
bbutler@fs.fed.us
